{"tid":347800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[未來交通]Hyperloop One完成第二次測試，時速達310公里創新高","createTime":"2017-08-05T06:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T14:33:06.000Z","uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"885ade8547e0b756b2c554eaf701c62ee366bf41","tid":347800,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"未來超級高鐵Hyperloop One日前成功完成第二階段測試，並創下了時速新紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHyperloop One於29日在美國拉斯維加斯外的一個沙漠地區進行測試，並成功在一條500米長的真空管道中滑行一個名為XP-1 的運輸艙。運輸艙更創下了時速192英里（約310公里）的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/hyperloop-one.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Fhyperloop-one.jpg&h=ef23c287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n團隊表示，測試所用的管道經過減壓處理，最高可在海拔20萬米中運作。這成績比起首階段所達到的113公里還要高出近3倍。至於XP-1長28英尺，用了磁懸浮技術作主要原理，可在行走過程中大幅減低空氣阻力。另外，它又用了碳和鋁纖維所製成，使艙身更輕盈。理論上，XP-1最高時速可達760英里（約1223公里）。<br />\n<br />\n目前，Hyperloop One仍需進行一系列的測試，確保運輸艙不會在行走過程中失壓以致發生意外。而在下一階段的測試中，Hyperloop One目標為提升速度，務求達到時速402公里（約250英里）。正式投入營運後，Hyperloop One的理想速度更可達每小時500英里（約805公里）。"},{"pid":"ecb4405b131e4bc9ae75153233a4170a19f0622e","tid":347800,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"310公里攞出來講<br />\n<br />\n笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b2e2ff66f8a383a09232ea8bc07fd2b0b9989f","tid":347800,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>310公里攞出來講<br />\n<br />\n笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第二次測試就310公里好明顯未到極限啦..."},{"pid":"a5e7acdc6928b7f002f7081c32b4b134cbde0b6b","tid":347800,"uid":48442,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c171b710d91b290518d74987228ac08d93f3996","tid":347800,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸高鐵閒閒地700kmh啦（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n大陸2016試緊果架CIT500都仲係最快600kmh..2017年咁快有700kmh投產仲要閒閒地?"},{"pid":"921b048d83219d95791dda456127639fd8867389","tid":347800,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大陸高鐵閒閒地700kmh啦（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n大陸2016試緊果架CIT500都仲係最快600kmh..2017年咁快有700kmh投產仲要閒閒地?</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最最重要係Hloop以後普及，成本連維修點都唔洗燒過千億兼遠遠快撚過呢條香港去深圳既短鳩動車囉！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4d6f634c340d487e836b817963d1df0774697e","tid":347800,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48767892599a479875127bcf77d225e78f347336","tid":347800,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"805...."},{"pid":"99b9ea6f79029bd98b088c0dc09e279f4db2d7f8","tid":347800,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母仲高鐵 依條野都平過高鐵香港段"},{"pid":"3ea23a12b82936af1cc86d884ba721fa9ab2224b","tid":347800,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"310公里就唔好論啦。 日本Maglev 有風阻都603啦。"},{"pid":"056eda16133b762c90b63d7db02e492a6b07c1e3","tid":347800,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"又係美國<br />\n有咩突破9成都係美國<br />\n支那都係比個土地日本啦<br />\n唔好累人累物"},{"pid":"c3953f9b0c34bc5f2e7386ac71541bd487